[[!meta title="New Staff Checklist"]]
# Things to do when you become...

## New Staff

* [[Set up a wiki account|ikiwiki/editing-the-wiki]]
* Add yourself to the [[staff list|staff]]
* Get permission to push to the [OCF GitHub repository](https://github.com/OCF)
* Be added to staff group on the [bug tracker](https://rt.ocf.berkeley.edu/)
* Be mentored on using puppet

## Semi-Root Staff

* Be granted a kerberos root principal

## Root Staff

* Be added to group admin

## Site Manager

* Be granted a kerberos admin principal
